Package: ReportGenerator
Type: Package
Title: Automatic Report Generator of Darwin EU Studies
Version: 1.17.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cesar", "Barboza", , "c.barboza@darwin-eu.org", role = c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-4453-3071")),
    person("Ger", "Inberg", , "g.inberg@darwin-eu.org", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Generates automatic reports in Word format from Data Analysis and Real World Interrogation Network (DARWIN EU) study results. Includes a Shiny interface and accepts data from incidence, prevalence, drug utilisation and treatment patterns studies. Creates tables and figures in the report in accordance to the Catalogue of Standard Analyses.
